short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Raise money for charities that focus on developing Armenia and Artsakh's infrastructure with each tab you open.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Raise money to donate to Armenia and Artsakh with each tab you open on your browser!

HyeTab transforms your browser's "new tab" page. Each time you open a new tab, you will be greeted with an Armenia-themed new tab with pictures from Armenia and Artsakh, widgets, and a couple of banner ads. These banner ads are HyeTab’s only source of revenue. The generated revenue is donated to charities and projects in the homeland with 100% transparency.

HyeTab is a community of people who care about Armenia and Artsakh and continue to raise funds for the homeland doing their day-to-day activities.

Learn more at https://hyetab.io.

Your privacy matters to us - HyeTab is committed to protecting your privacy. We don’t collect or sell any data. For more info checkout our privacy policy at: https://hyetab.io/privacy.
